### System Requirements

Kreuzberg requires:

- **Python 3.10+** (Python binding)
- **Node.js 16+** (TypeScript/Node.js binding)
- **Go 1.19+** (Go binding)
- **Java 11+** (Java binding)
- **Ruby 2.7+** (Ruby binding)
- **PHP 8.0+** (PHP binding)
- **C# .NET 6.0+** (C# binding)
- **.NET 6.0+** (C# binding)

Optional: [ONNX Runtime](https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/releases) version 1.21 or lower for embeddings support.
